{"tid":1822630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教署百周年Cosplay冇特務警察份？","createTime":"2020-01-13T05:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:53:29.000Z","uid":7439,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7e0a213ae9c6a805b31f48416c8b486d8b48c4","tid":1822630,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"懲教署為慶祝部門踏入一百周年，該署今日（一月十二日）於中環大館舉行「懲教署一百周年慶典啟動禮」暨嘉年華活動。圖示懲教人員穿着懷舊與現行的制服。<br />\n在嘉年華活動方面，大會設置不同攤位遊戲，並安排懲教人員穿着懷舊制服，讓市民拍照留念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3844081/org/f996be6c5cfea063b6f4489215b2d4d9.jpg/VEEycciMoq4ECGn9lvvYEJ9ahcUVbxLYWD9qB1g_agc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3844081%2Forg%2Ff996be6c5cfea063b6f4489215b2d4d9.jpg%2FVEEycciMoq4ECGn9lvvYEJ9ahcUVbxLYWD9qB1g_agc&h=680efbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3844086/org/5521a6c34563e0f6ed1d1cda95d75f4d.jpg/fEtC7BlzwJZagzV6VPTHqhT4jYGXPUY8v5cSN7-XEjc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3844086%2Forg%2F5521a6c34563e0f6ed1d1cda95d75f4d.jpg%2FfEtC7BlzwJZagzV6VPTHqhT4jYGXPUY8v5cSN7-XEjc&h=d819f46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇特務警察份？<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/cnt/news/20191116/photo/bkn-20191116102351073-1116_00822_001_02p.jpg?20191117041847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191116%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191116102351073-1116_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20191117041847&h=99bbb816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/12/%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-%E6%87%B2%E6%95%99%E7%BD%B2-20191201190943_2dec_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E6%2587%25B2%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%25B